Self thoughts
-------------

Ce que je cherche: épanouissement, apaisement, sérénité
Apprivoi
Ce qui te rassure: besoin d'une sensation de controle.
How did you arrive there:
- anxiety Babou
- stress work
-> deep feeling of unbalance, loss of control, loss of purpose

Mindfulness is living the present moment and not living with your thoughts. 
This is not to be applied all the time, otherwise you don't think about important things which make who you are, 
help you analyze situations and take decisions. And make things go ahead for instance at work by having ideas at random times. 
So you do need to have these moments where you're in your thoughts. 
The whole point is to manage to distinguish which thoughts are positive because they are constructive and make you go ahead, 
and which thoughts are negative and useless and just make you feel depressed -> the famous mental looping about things you can't change.
Also distinguish what you can change from what you can't, and focus only on the one you can (stoicism, Tim Ferriss).
